<%- include('partials/head', { title, active }) %>
<%- include('partials/nav', { user, active }) %>
<section class="hero grid two">
  <div>
    <p class="eyebrow">MongoDB · Socket.IO · EVE SDE JSONL</p>
    <h1>一个带账号、市场、舰队、工业和囤积经济的像素挂机搜打撤网络游戏。</h1>
    <p class="lead">服务端权威计算离线收益，客户端只负责显示；SDE 导入后会变成星系、舰船、装备、材料、蓝图、价格和掉落表。</p>
    <div class="actions">
      <% if (user) { %>
        <a class="button" href="/command">进入指挥室</a>
      <% } else { %>
        <a class="button" href="/register">创建克隆体</a>
        <a class="button ghost" href="/login">登录账号</a>
      <% } %>
    </div>
    <div class="demo-box">
      <b>本地演示账号</b><br>
      玩家：<code>demo / demo1234</code>　管理员：<code>admin / admin1234</code>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="hero-card">
    <img src="/public/assets/landing_hero.png" alt="pixel hero">
    <div class="status-grid">
      <div><b><%= pilots %></b><span>已注册飞行员</span></div>
      <div><b>8</b><span>核心页面</span></div>
      <div><b>∞</b><span>SDE 可扩展内容</span></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
<section class="grid three feature-row">
  <article class="panel"><h3>搜打撤</h3><p>扫描、跃迁、战斗/采集、战利品装舱、风险阈值自动撤离、入站入库或卖出。</p></article>
  <article class="panel"><h3>囤积经济</h3><p>锁仓、保留量、市场价差、区域套利、库存容量、精炼和制造让“屯什么”变成策略。</p></article>
  <article class="panel"><h3>多人网络</h3><p>账号登录、会话保存在 MongoDB，Socket.IO 广播在线玩家、舰队、聊天和世界事件。</p></article>
</section>
<section class="panel">
  <h2>最近星域事件</h2>
  <div class="event-list">
    <% for (const event of events) { %>
      <div class="event <%= event.severity %>"><b><%= event.title %></b><span><%= event.message %></span><time><%= shortDate(event.createdAt) %></time></div>
    <% } %>
    <% if (!events.length) { %><p class="muted">还没有世界事件，启动游戏循环后会逐渐出现。</p><% } %>
  </div>
</section>
<%- include('partials/footer') %>
